duties_responsibilities.duty: Evaluate and analyze web content, including images and videos, to improve search result accuracy and enhance user experience.
Participate in a long-term project commitment of 10-15 hours per week, contributing to the improvement of innovative AI systems.
Provide reliable training data to enhance AI technology in various industries, including technology, automotive, financial services, retail, healthcare, and governments.
Join a global network of skilled contributors to curate training data and improve AI technology worldwide.
Use a smartphone and Gmail address, and pass a qualification exam to qualify for the role as a resident of the United States.
